column3: text
I am looking for a particular attraction called The Place. I need more information about it.
Sure. It is a nightclub in the south area. Do you need the address or phone number?
Just the postcode and entrance fee I am afraid.
22 sidney street is the address
Could you please tell me the postcode?
Of course, sorry about that. The postcode is cb23hg. Can I be of any further assistance to you today?
What is the entrance fee for it?
Unfortunately, I am not sure of the entrance fee to The Place. You can call them to find out: 01223324600.
Thank you. I will also need a train from Cambridge to London Kings Cross on Tuesday, would you be able to help me?
I need some more information first. Is there a specific time you would like to leave or arrive by?
I would like the train to arrive by 16:00.
There are five trains that will arrive by 16:00, the train that arrives closes to that time is TR315 which arrives at 13:51
That one will work. Can you book it for 4 people?
I booked your train for 4 people. The reference number is T6X9JMIA and the total fee is 94.4 GBP. Is there anything else I can help you with?
Does this train help those with a disability?
Yes, this train provides assistance for those with disability. Anything else I can do for you?
Got it. Is there a charge to use WiFi on the train?
Yes, WiFi is available and it is free of charge. Could I help you with anything else?
can I stay connected to the internet on this train?
Yes, you can use basic WiFi by connecting to GreatNorthern_WiFi. Is there anything else I can help you with?
That will be everything. Thank you for you help.
OVERALL
I need a three star hotel with internet. Can you help?
I'm sorry, I cannot help you with hotels. Are you sure that's what you're looking for?
I'm sorry. I meant to ask for information on a restaurant. It's called the Stazione Restaurant and Coffee Bar.
The stazione restaurant is an expensive, italian restaurant located in the centre area. Would you like me to make you a booking today?
Yes, sounds wonderful. Can you book a table for 7 at 12:00 on Saturday?
The booking was successful. Your table will be reserved for 15 minutes and your reference number is TA6XS4CY.
Does it have vegetarian options?
Yes, they have both vegan and vegetarian dishes. What else may I help you with?
Can i get free wifi here?
The Sazione Restaurant and Coffee Bar doesn't offer free wifi at this time. What are you interested in trying?
Great. I also need to find an attraction in the center and would like to know what type, address and entrance fee you find.
Okay what kind of attraction are you looking for?
Anything you'd recommend, as long as it's in the centre.
I recommend the vue cinema, it's got a lot of great features to watch!
Sounds good! Could I have the address and entrance fee, please?
Address is the grafton centre, east road, I do not know the entrance fee.
Thanks! Do you have a phone number so I can find the entrance fee.
The phone number is 08712240240.
Can you tell me what credit cards Stazione accepts?
They will accept American Express, Mastercard, and Visa credit cards. Do you have any other questions?
Thank you! And this is a cinema attraction?
Yes it is. Is there anything else I can do for you?
I don't need anything else.
OVERALL
Hello, I'm trying to find an international restaurant in the east. Any ideas?
Yes, the missing sock is an international restaurant in the east in the cheap price range. Would you like a reservation?
No, please give me their post code instead.
The post code is cb259aq.
I also need a hotel on the Southside.
I have 1 hotel called the lensfield hotel located on 53-57 lensfield road.
When is the checkin time?
The check in time is 14:00. Would you like for me to book it for you?
Can you tell me if it offers free parking? Also, how many stars is the Lensfield?
The Lenfield is a 3 star hotel. They do offer free parking.
Can you look for a 2 star hotel in that area if not available then could you try one that is in the east?
There is one located in the east, express by holiday inn cambridge. It has free internet and parking, would you like to book?
Is there a hotel lift?
There is a lift located on the Express by Holiday Inn Cambridge property. Would you like for me to book it for you?
Yes I'd like to book 5 nights for 1 beginning on Tuesday. Could I get the reference number for that as well?
How many guests will be staying?
Just one, thanks.
You are all set, the reference number is 9WZD62FF, anything else that I can assist with?
What are the nearest diners by the hotel?
There is a Missing Sock off of Finders Corner Newmarket Road. it looks to be cheap, and is in the east side of the city.
Actually, I'd like to book a taxi from the hotel to The Missing Sock. I'd like to depart by 09:15.
Sure, I found you a blue Tesla, their contact number is 07980198100. Can I assist you with anything else?
Can I change my booking if my plan changes?
You can cancel 24 hours in advance. After that only minor changes can be made. Would you like any more information?
No, thank you. Goodbye.
OVERALL
I am looking for information in Cambridge.
You really should be including something to search for instead of a general statement, what do you want me to search for?
Wow, you are snippy for an Info centre! Perhaps a museum.
I apologize for my early snappiness. I'd be happy to find a museum for you to visit while your here. Is there a particular area of town you'd like?
No, I'd just like to visit a museum, could you recommend one to me?
I highly recommend the Lynne Strover Gallery in the west. They have free admission. They are located at 23 High Street, Fen Ditton.
Thanks! I also need a train to Peterborough on Saturday, please. I need to leave after 18:00.
can i book it for you?
Please, I'll need 3 tickets.
Where are you departing from?
I am leaving from Cambridge.
TR5194 arrives in peterborough at 17:56. Is that cutting it too close or would you like to book that one?
No, I need to leave Cambridge after 18:00.
I've booked 3 tickets on the TR2569 departing at 18:34. The total is 39.59 GBP, payable at the station. Reference# 6DX0OQTC. Can I help with anything else?
Is there a place to park a bike at the departure station?
Yes, bicycle parking spots are available at the station. Can I be of any other assistance?
Is there a way to bring my bike onto the train?
Yes, it has to be able to be folded. Will you be needing anything else.
No that is it. Thank you.
OVERALL
I need to find a hotel in Cambridge that's moderately priced. I don't need to have free parking included for my stay.
There are four possibilities, one is a hotel and the others are guesthouses. Do you have a preference for one or the other?
I do not. Are any of those places located in the centre?
Only one is located in the centre. The cityroomz which also has free wifi. Would you be interested in booking this hotel?
Yes, that sounds splendid. I would like to book a room there for 6 people for 2 nights, and I would like the reference number, please.
What night would you like to begin your stay?
I would like to stay starting Tuesday night
I have booked the cityroomz hotel for 2 nights, starting this Tuesday, for 6 people.
What does the hotel charge for parking?
No, the hotel does not charge for parking. Does that work for you?
That is great! How much?
I apologize I don't have the price. It is in the moderate price range however.
Do you know if this hotel also charge for wifi separately?
Yes, the charge for wifi at Cityroomz is 5 GP/Day. I have taken care of everything for you for your reservation.
I see. That sounds great. Thank you. Could I get a reference number please?
Your reference number is : EB05KFXV. Will there be anything else today?
I also need a restaurant that serves turkish food please.
There are three Turkish restaurants, all in the center of town. The Meze Bar is expensive, but the other two are more moderate. Would you like to book a table?
Are there any gluten free foods offered there?
There is not a gluten-free menu at the Meze Bar. Is that acceptable for you?
the meze bar is fine. book it for 6 at 14:15 on tuesday
Your table will be reserved for 15 minutes. The reference number is XZX9AGML.
Thank you so much!
OVERALL
I am looking for a train to Stansted airport.
Finding a train into the stansted airport will not be a problem. Do you have a departure point in mind?
I will be leaving from Cambridge and just need to arrive by 14:30.
There are 63 trains that fit that criteria. Is there a specific day you need to leave?
Right. Tuesday. Sorry.
No worries! I have TR8714 departing Cambridge at 13:40 and arriving at Stansted Airport at 14:08. Will that work for you?
Can I bring my bike on the train?
You can bring a bike on the train if it is the foldable kind. Do you need any other information?
Yes. I am also looking for a place to stay on the north side of Cambridge. The hotel can have a 0 star rating.
City Centre North B&B is a cheap guesthouse on the north side. It has free wifi and free parking.
Does City Centre North B&B offer a concierge service for guests?
Sorry, there is no concierge service at this hotel. Do you still wish to book here?
That sounds perfect! I will take it.
When would you like to make your reservation for, and for how many people?
Oh, my mistake, I don't want a booking, just the information.
Absolutely! The City Centre North B and B is located at 328a Histon Road, postcode cb43ht. Their number is 01223312843. Can I help you with anything else today?
One more thing: is there a fitness center there?
There are no fitness centers onsite. Did you still want to book there?
Yes, I would like to book starting Friday, for four nights and five people please.
I'm sorry, I could not make that booking. Would you be able to book another day or have a shorter stay?
What about for only 3 nights?
Booking was successful for 3 nights at city centre north b and b starting on Friday. Your reference number is VJKBCF6E. Can I help with anything else?
No, that will do it. Thanks for your help!
OVERALL
We want to explore a park in Cambridge.
We have 5 parks. Do you have a certain area in mind?
I would like it to be in the south part of town. Please provide their phone number, postcode, and entrance fee. Thanks.
You can visit Wandlebury country park. The address is wandlebury ring, gog magog hills, babraham and the post code is cb223ae.
What is the phone number and how much does it cost to get in ?
There is no entrance fee. The phone number is 01223243830. Is there anything else you need?
I also need a train that will depart from cambridge and should go to london kings cross.
How about train TR5767 that leaves at 05:00 on Friday?
No, that doesn't work for me. I need a train that leaves after 11:00 on Wednesday
Train TR9781 leaves at 11:00 on Wednesday would you like me to book that train for you?
Am I able to reserve a seat on that train?
No, seat reservation is not possible. Can I help with something else?
Will there be wifi service on the train, and if so, what is the cost?
WiFi service is available at no charge. Do you want me to book you a ticket?
Yep I only need one ticket and the reference number please.
Booking was successful, the total fee is 23.6 GBP payable at the station . Reference number is : Q7Q9W4IN. is there anything else i can help you with?
No thanks. That's all I needed.
Okay, let us know if you need anything else.
That was all thanks for your help today.
OVERALL
While in Cambridge I need to find a restaurant called the rice boat.
Rice Boat is located at 37 Newnham Road in Newnham. Would you like to book a reservation?
Yes please, I need a table for 6 on Sunday at 17:45.
Wonderful. You're table is reserved for 15 minutes. The reference number is JM6MM56Y.
I'm also looking for a moderately priced 2 star hotel with free wifi in the south.
I was not able to find any hotels matching those requirements.
Can you try in the north then?
I was not able to find any hotels matching those requirements.
Is there any moderately priced hotels in the city centre then? I need a hotel for the same group of people for 5 nights starting the same day.
Looks like there was an error in our system earlier. There are two moderately priced hotels in the north - The Ashley and The Lovell Lodge.
What is the minimum age to check in?
You must be 18 to check in. Would you like to book at either of these places?
Could you try to book us there for 4 nights instead?
Yes, which of the two would you prefer? Ashley Hotel or Lovell Lodge?
The Lovell Lodge sounds nice. Please try for 5 nights but we can settle with 4 if we need to.
How many people is the hotel for and which day would you like to begin your trip on?
Oh sure, It's for 5 nights starting sunday for 6 people please.
I'm sorry there is nothing available on those days. Would you like to shorten your stay or try the other hotel?
Can you try the other hotel then?
I was not able to book that one either. Can we try a different day perhaps?
Do they have vegetarian options?
There are some vegetarian entrees available yes. Do you want a table there?
Can you try booking for 4 nights instead?
I was able to book the Lovell Lodge for 4 nights starting Sunday for six people. The reference number is XTY5KJI9.
Does the hotel offer concierge services for guests?
I am sorry but Lovell Lodge does not have a concierge service for guests. Can I do anything else for you?
Thank you very much! That was everything i needed. Take care and have a great day.
OVERALL
I need a train leaving broxbourne on wednesday. Can you book it for me?
Sure! What is your destination?
I need to arrive in Cambridge by 11:45.
I have train TR1819 that leaves at 10:32 and arrives in Cambridge at 11:32. Would that work for you?
First, I need to know if my dog who will be with me is allowed on the train.
You are permitted to bring two pets, but they are to be kept on a short leash. Would you like any more assistance?
Yes, can you tell me if there are size limits for dogs on the train?
They must be able to be carried in a basket sized 85x60x60cm. Do you have any other questions?
I'd also like to purchase additional data beyond what is offered on their wifi service, can I do that?
There is no additional data available for purchase. Is that okay?
yeah, what's the price of the tickets?
The price of the tickets is 17.90 pounds. Shall I make a booking for you?
Yes, please. I'm also looking for a hotel that's cheap and in the north.
There are no cheap hotels in the north but there are 2 guesthouses. Will those work?
That sounds fine.
Which one would you be interested in? I recommend Worth House because it is 4 stars.
Actually, can you try a moderate price hotel in the north instead? Sorry for the trouble.
We have 11 options that meet your criteria. Would you like to narrow it down by stars, internet, or parking?
Yeah, I don't need internet. Other than that, could you just recoomend one that has a reasonable number of stars?
How about the alpha-milton guest house? It's in the north and moderately priced.
that will be fine. book it for me
How many people and for how many nights?
book it for 2 people and 5 nights starting from the same day.
I will book it for you now.
What is the check-in time?
its between 1.00 p.m and 7.00 pm Is there anything else you need?
Thank you . I will also need the booking reference number.
Booking was successful. Reference number is : XML9YIR2.
Great! Thank you that's all I needed!
I see the train was not booked. Would you like me to book it now?
Please do so, thank you. After that, I need a cheap hotel.
How many tickets in total would you like me to purchase for you on train TR1819?
I need it for 2 people.
Okay! I was able to book that for you and your reference number is AMA9OE5J.
Okay. Thank you so much for help.
OVERALL
I am looking for something entertaining in town later and I've got some things in mind.
What are your ideas? what area of town and what type of attraction?
I'm looking for a theatre in the centre.
There are four theatres in Centre: ADC Theatre, Cambridge Arts Theatre, Mumford Theatre and The Cambridge Corn Exchange. Would you be interested in any of these?
Cambridge Arts sounds good, can I get the phone number? Is there any entrance fee? And then a nice expensive dinner in the same area please.
Cambridge arts theatre phone is 0122350333, no entrance fee information is available. There are 33 restaurants in your price range, do you have a food type preference?
Yes, I like there to be Cuban food.
I am sorry but there are no Cuban restaurants available. Would like another type of food?
Hmm, I'll try Japanese instead.
we have wagamama located in 36 Saint Andrews Street. can i book for you?
Does this restaurant allow BYOB?
No, bringing one's own alcohol is not allowed at the restaurant. Can I help you locate the restaurant?
No thank you I just need the postcode.
The post code is cb23ar. Is there anything else I can help with?
Can you book me a taxi that will pick me up from Cambridge Arts Theatre at 07:15 and take me to Wagamama?
Booking completed! Booked car type : grey volkswagen Contact number : 07275251696 Can I help with anything else today?
Will I be able to cancel in case my plans change?
You can, as long as you do it within 24 hours. You will be charged thereafter. Anything else today?
How much will the charge be for cancelling it?
The charge is 10 GBP after the cancellation period. Is there anything else I can help you with?
That will be all today. Thank you.
OVERALL
Hi there. Can you help me find a train to Cambridge on Thursday?
I can. Will you be departing from London Kings Cross?
No, I'm coming from Ely.
What time would you like to travel?
I would like to arrive in Cambridge by 16:15.
I would recommend the TR7745 train that arrives at 07:52. Would that work?
I need the travel time for that.
It is 17 minutes.
Okay, if you book it can I change my ticket later if needed?
No, you would need to get the ticket refunded and then buy a new one. Is there anything else I can help with?
Does the train have WiFi service that I can use while riding?
Yes there will be wifi on the train. Log on with ID GreatNorthern_WiFi. Would you like any other info?
can you see about reservations at the aylesbray lodge guest house
Yes, I can. Will it be for for just 1 night?
Do you have to pay to park in their parking lot there?
The parking in this establishment is free. How else can I help you today?
Actually, let's not worry about booking it just now. Can you narrow down where it is for me with the area at postcode?
Sure. It's in the south of town with postcode cb17sr. Can I help you with anything else?
No, that seems like everything. Go ahead and book it, and we should be done here.
How many nights will you be staying?
I'm sorry, I'm not ready to book yet. I can do it myself later. Thanks so much for all of your help. Bye.
OVERALL
Hi, I will be in Cambridge soon and need a place to stay that has free parking.
I have 29 results for places to stay with free parking, what area are you looking to stay in?
I am not particular about the area but it should be a hotel and 0 stars please.
Unfortunately, I do not have any matches for your request.
How about a guesthouse with free parking and 0 stars?
There are 2 options for guesthouses with 0 stars and free parking, the City Centre North B and B, and the El Shaddai
I'd like to book El Shaddai, 3 people for 4 nights, starting from Tuesday.
Unfortunately, the hotel was unable to accommodate that stay. We can try fewer days, or beginning on a different day, if you like.
Let`s try the beginning of a different day than.
Sorry, I'm afraid a different day wouldn't work, either. Perhaps you'd like a shorter stay?
Is there front desk open 24 hours?
No, the El Shaddai front desk is not open 24 hours. How many nights would you like me to make your reservation for?
How about 3 nights, then?
I was able to book your party for a 3 day stay starting on Tuesday. Your reference number is TJ4K62L2. Is there anything else I can help you with?
Yes, I also need a train leaving after 9:15 on Tuesday from Kings lynn to Cambridge.
There are 14 options. When would you like to arrive by?
It doesn't matter. I just need to leave Kings Lynn after 9:15.
TR1704 will have you there by 10:58. Would you like me to book that for you?
How much will that cost me. I am on a budget.
9.80 pounds. I can book that for you, if you like.
Does this train allow you to purchase additional data on their wifi service?
No, you will not be able to purchase any additional data. Can I make the reservation for you?
Thank you but I will book it myself. This is all I needed, you were great thanks again!!
OVERALL
I was looking for a hotel in the center of town that offers free parking.
I found the Gonville Hotel and University Arms Hotel that meets your criteria.
Is the hotel expensive, and is it a guesthouse?
The Gonville Hotel and University Arms Hotel is expensive, but it is not a guesthouse. The guesthouses that meet your criteria are cheap.
Okay, how about any hotels that are expensive that has free parking.
There are no hotels that match that requirement.
How about a hotel type instead of guesthouse?
There are 2 results for expensive hotels in town centre. One is the gonville hotel, the other university arms hotel. Would you like to book one of these?
Yes please book Gonville Hotel for 2 people for 4 nights starting tuesday
I am sorry. That hotel is unavailable for your requested stay. Would you like to pick a different day or shorter stay?
Okay, but first can you tell me if you have any restrictions for kids?
Yes, kids are allowed at this hotel. Would you like to proceed with the booking?
Can you first tell me whether the hotel provides an in-room safety deposit box for guest's valuables?
Yes, this establishment offers safety deposit boxes in its rooms. Is there anything else I can do for you today?
Can you try 3 nights instead?
I have booked the Gonville hotel for 3 nights. The reference number is 4QYJH7Y5. Can I help you with anything else?
Yes, are there any modern american restaurants in the center of town? Something expensive.
Sorry, but there aren't any restaurants that meet those criteria. Something less expensive, perhaps?
How about a modern european restaurant?
Yes, I can recommend darrys cookhouse and wine shop. Would you like me to make a reservation?
Yes I want a reservation for 2 people at 14:30
Which day would you like the reservation for?
Will there be enough seating for babies?
Yes, they do have available high chairs for your convenience. May I make a reservation there for you?
Tuesday please. Also I need the booking reference number when you are done please.
Booking confirmed! The reference number is Z7E6UORT. Can I help you with anything else today?
No that's all. Thank you.
OVERALL
I want to find a moderately priced restaurant that serves british food. What is the address and phone number?
There are 5 moderately price restaurants that serve British food. Is there an area of town that would work best for you?
I do not care. Please suggest one.
saint johns chop house serves british food, is in the west area of town and is in the moderate price range
What is their address and phone number?
the phone number is 01223353110 and the address is 21-24 Northampton Street, is there anything else I can help you with?
Can you tell me if they have a bar there?
You are able to get alcohol at Saint Johns Chop House. Is there anything else you need to know?
Does this restaurant offer take out?
Unfortunately, this establishment does not offer takeout service. How else can I help you today?
Does saint johns chop house have free WiFi for customers?
Yes, Saint Johns Chop House have free WiFi for customers. Is there anything else I can assist you with?
No, thank you, goodbye.
OVERALL
How much does it cost to take the bus in Cambridge?
Where will you be traveling to?
I will be traveling to london.
The rate for a trip from Cambridge to london kings cross ranges from 18.88 pounds to 23.60 pounds depending on the day of travel.
I am also looking for a hotel in the west side of Cambridge. Can you help me?
There are a few to choose from. Do you prefer a hotel or a guesthouse?
I want a hotel on the west side that doesn't have to include internet. If no internet, what about free wifi?
Unfortunately there are no hotels meeting your criteria. Would you like me to look in another part of town?
Are you sure that there are no hotels on the west side of town? With or without internet?
There are four. Do you have a price range in mind?
No price preference, whatever you recommend.
Finches bed and breakfast is a cheap guesthouse in the west with a 4 star rating. It has internet and parking. Would you like me to book this?
Does is charge a fee if you want to stay with pets?
There is no fee because pets are not allowed. Should I book it for you still?
Yes please book for 7 people for 5 nights starting from monday.
You are booked at Finches Bed and Breakfast. Your reference number is LMAP8LOO. Is there anything else I can help you with?
I also need to book passage on a train on friday, from cambridge to birmingham new street.
What time do you want to depart?
It needs to leave sometime after 15:45, and I'll need 7 tickets.
Is there a particular time you would like to arrive by?
I would like to make a reservation for a seat on the train, is that possible?
We do not offer seat reservation. Would you like to book the train?
Does this train offer additional wifi data packages?
There is no additional WIFI Data to buy. Is there anything else I can do for you today?
nope, would just like it to leave after 15:45
Booking was successful, the total fee is 525.69 GBP payable at the station . Reference number is : ZTJU607W. Anything more I can help with?
That will be all. Thanks for your help! Bye!
OVERALL
I'm looking for a restaurant recommendation.
I would love to assist. Do you have a price range in mind?
Yes, I am looking for a expensive scottish restaurant.
Sorry there are no records matching your request. Would you like to change your request?
Okay, let's try for an expensive Italian restaurant instead.
I have 5 different ones. 4 are in the centre of town and 1 is in the south. Do you have a preference?
No, I just need a resrvation for 7 people at 17:45 on monday.
Okay. Your booking was successful. Your reference number is 42WW4454. The table will be reserved for 15 minutes.
Does this restaurant have delivery service?
There is no delivery service at Frankie and Bennys. Can I assist with anything else?
Well, can I order for takeout at this restaurant?
I'm sorry, they do not. You will have to eat in the restaurant. Could I help you find something else?
No although I need to know, do they have accommodations for persons with disabilities?
Frankie and Bennys is wheelchair accessible. What else do you need to know about the restaurant?
Thank you. Could you help me find a museum that is in the east?
Yes, you might want to try the gallery at twelve a high street in fulbourn.
Thank you so much. Do you know if there is an admission charge?
Great news, admission is free for that museum. Anything else I can help you with today?
Can you also tell me the phone number and postcode?
Their phone number is 01223295264, and postcode is cb15dh.
Great! Thank you for all your help.
Thank you for allowing me to help you, have a great day.
You too! Thanks.
OVERALL
Hi, I am looking for a restaurant. I would prefer an expensive restaurant in the west of the city.
We offer 9 such places.
Is there a British one available?
Great choice! I have two. Graffiti and travellers rest. Would you like me to book one of these?
I am looking for some rest as a traveler so I choose travellers rest. There will be four of us for Saturday at 11:00. Please book.
I'm sorry, it seems they are unable to accommodate you at that day and time. Would you like me to try another?
First, can you tell me if this restaurant offers complimentary wifi for its guests?
The hotel does have free wifi available. Would you like to book a reservation?
I do need to make sure that there is access for my wheelchair, does the restaurant help with that?
This restaurant is wheelchair accessible, I can confirm. Can I help you find anything else?
Can you try for 10:00 please?
A table is reserved for 10:00. Your reference number is TX8BTBJT. The table will be reserved for 15 minutes. May I help you with anything else?
I would also like to find a college to visit.
What area is this college in? Do you know the name of it?
Is there a college on the west side of town by the restaurant travellers rest? I will need the college's address and phone number, too.
How about Queen's College? It is on the west side of town. The phone number is 01223335511 and address is Silver Street.
Yes! I would also like to book a taxi.
I can certainly help you with that! Where would you like to be picked up and dropped off, and at what time?
I would like to be picked up at Queen's College on Silver street and taken to Traveler's West. I want to make the reservation on time.
Okay, I've got a grey skoda booked for you.
Could you provide a contact number? Thanks!
The contact number is 07334374879. Is there something else I can assist with?
Yes, I know we'll be going through a toll gate, will I have to pay extra for that?
All toll fees and taxes are included you can't tip if you would like. Is there anything else you would like me to look up for you?
Great that is all I needed thank you for your help today.
OVERALL
i need a place to stay in Cambridge thats 4 star with free wifi
the a and b guest house is a great place
Do this hotel offer free parking also?
Unfortunately this guest house doesn't offer parking, would you like me to search for similar hotels that offer parking?
Yes I do. When you find it, I need 3 nights for 5 people starting on Wednesday. I'll take the reference number too.
I'm sorry, there are no hotels that meet your criteria. Would you like to try searching for something else?
There are seriously no 4 star hotels with free wifi and free parking in all of Cambridge? I'm pretty sure there should be.
The arbury lodge guesthouse is 4 stars, it has internet it is in the moderate price range
Does this hotel's front desk operate 24 hours a day?
No, the front desk doesn't operate 24 hours a day. Do you have any other questions about the hotel?
Yes, I also will be travelling with my daughter and some hotels restrict staying with children. Will my daughter be allowed at this hotel?
Children are not permitted to stay here What other options are you interested in?
Great! Could you book it for 5 people and 3 nights starting from wednesday?
Sorry for the confusion, I have that booked for you, your reference # is: HQSOZLWH. Can I help you with anything else today?
Do I need to make parking reservations in advance?
No, reservations in advance are not necessary. Anything else for you today?
how about one that is in the type of nightclub.
There's the club ballare which is rather nice. Would you like some more information about it?
